horized to work in the U.S.	{"apply": "True", "salary": "See application for details.", "summary": "This software engineering position at Modern Treasury focuses on building core infrastructure for their payment and ledger products, involving complex data architectures and high reliability systems. The role includes working on the API, web platform, and embracing open source tools. The job requires experience in web application development, SQL/Relational databases, containerization, and cloud-native deployments. The company values equal employment opportunity and diversity.", "location": "San Francisco, New York", "reasoning": "The job is applicable because it requires 3+ years of experience and does not have explicit degree requirements.", "department": null, "tech_stack": ["Ruby on Rails", "React", "GraphQL", "Tailwind CSS", "Postgres", "Redis", "AWS", "Docker", "GitHub", "Buildkite"]}
